Default values were not handled in AlteredSliceTag.

Related to https://github.com/apache/incubator-superset/pull/3668/files

@Mogball

in explore view, controls like color csheme, legend, rich tooltip, etc., change these controls should see effect instantly, without click Run Query.

Instant controls are just for re-render without Run Query (no ajax request triggered). I update `Chart` property `lastRendered` with a new timestamp, so that react can pick up this change and call `renderViz`
@michellethomas @mistercrunch

Set healthcheck for envoy to integrate and check service health. Easier for us to add endpoint vs. switching envoys reference.

https://github.com/lyft/incubator-superset/pull/2

@mistercrunch

If you have a single dimension that is an extraction, e.g.
```javascript
{
    "outputName": "country_uppercase", 
    "extractionFn": {
      "type": "upper"
    }, 
    "type": "extraction", 
    "dimension": "country", 
    "outputType": "STRING"
}
```
And `order_desc` is set to true, the query results in an error because `dimension` is set to the dictionary value, instead of just the dimension name.
